title: Personal Nightmare 1989 PC - GoG
description:
Personal Nightmare from 1989 for Windows (XP, Vista, 7, 8).

Personal Nightmare is a survival horror adventure game. There is no direct plot, but the game focuses on a town where The Devil has invaded and the player has four days to eliminate all possessed citizens and purge the evil before it can take over.

Genre: adventure / fpp / horror
Release date: January 1, 1989
Compatible with: Windows (XP, Vista, 7, 8)
Languages: English
Developer / publisher: Horrorsoft / Adventure Soft
Game modes: single-player
